OL,13,Ffirms caps prices at roughly the same
OL,14,Flevel as households, but it will expire
OL,15,Fat the end of March.
OL,17,FOn Monday, Jeremy Hunt announced a new
OL,18,Fdiscounts scheme will take effect
OL,19,Fafterwards, lasting one year and
OL,20,Fapplying to all businesses and
OL,21,Fcharities.
